.TH HAWKPRO 1 "HawkPro v1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
HawkPro \- terminal-based Linux system process monitor

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B hawkpro
[\-\-uninstall]

.SH DESCRIPTION
HawkPro is a lightweight ncurses-based system monitor for Linux.
It displays real-time system metrics and a sortable process table
within a terminal interface.

.SH OPTIONS

.TP
.B \-\-uninstall
Uninstall HawkPro completely (removes binary, man page, and lifecycle manager).

.SH IN-APP CONTROLS
The following keyboard shortcuts are available while HawkPro is running:

.TP
.B C / c
Sort process table by CPU usage.

.TP
.B M / m
Sort process table by memory usage.

.TP
.B U / u
Sort process table by user.

.TP
.B Ctrl+F
Search for a process by name.

.TP
.B Q / q
Quit HawkPro.

